text: Mark Wills is an American country singer. In 1999 he had his first number one song on Hot Country Songs music chart. ==Early life== He was born on August 8, 1973 in Blue Ridge, Georgia. ==Discography== ;Singles "I Do (Cherish You)" (1998) ==Sources== Category:Country musicians from Georgia (U.S state) Category:People from Georgia (U.S. state) Category:1973 births Category:Living people
